OL,3,CCould your local election be delayed
OL,4,Cbecause of Labour's devolution plans?
OL,6,FOver half of England's 21 county
OL,7,Fcouncils could delay their local
OL,8,Felections due to happen in May, as a
OL,9,Fresult of Labour's changes to local
OL,10,Fgovernment.
OL,12,FIn a major shake-up of council
OL,13,Fstructures, the two-tier system of
OL,14,Fcounty councils and district councils
OL,15,Fcould be replaced by merging them
OL,16,Ftogether to create "unitary"
OL,17,Fauthorities. Labour say it will help
OL,18,Fthem to avoid duplication and give
OL,19,Fregions "a bigger voice".
