OL,6,FBut many are unhappy about the
OL,7,Fpotential delays - the District
OL,8,FCouncils network said people are being
OL,9,F"deprived of their local democracy",
OL,10,Fcalling the delays "unprecedented".
OL,12,FWhile Reform UK, which was expected to
OL,13,Fgain more seats at the elections in
OL,14,FMay, say Labour and the Conservatives
OL,15,F"are colluding to rob the British
OL,16,Fpeople of their democratic rights."
