OL,3,CCould your local election be delayed
OL,4,Cbecause of Labour's devolution plans?
OL,6,FThere are 21 county councils in
OL,7,FEngland, and 164 district councils.
OL,8,FAll county councils along with unitary
OL,9,Fcouncils and some regional mayors were
OL,10,Fdue to have elections in May, after
OL,11,Fdistrict and other types of councils
OL,12,Fheld their elections in May last year.
OL,14,FBut now at least half of those
OL,15,Fcouncils may not hold ballots at all,
OL,16,Fin order to smooth the transition
OL,17,Fprocess as they change their council
OL,18,Fstructure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
