OL,3,CCould your local election be delayed
OL,4,Cbecause of Labour's devolution plans?
OL,6,FBefore Christmas Rayner announced
OL,7,FLabour's "devolution revolution",
OL,8,Fpushing power out of Whitehall and
OL,9,Finto the hands of people with "skin in
OL,10,Fthe game" across a range of policy
OL,11,Fareas including housing.
OL,13,FThe Deputy PM said the Devolution
OL,14,FWhite Paper will ensure regional
OL,15,Fpowers are "no longer agreed at the
OL,16,Fwhim of a minister in Whitehall",
OL,17,Fpromising a mayor for every region of
OL,18,FEngland.
