OL,3,CCould your local election be delayed
OL,4,Cbecause of Labour's devolution plans?
OL,6,FOne of the key proposals in the White
OL,7,FPaper was creating larger authorities
OL,8,Fby scrapping two-tier council areas -
OL,9,Fand Friday marks the deadline for
OL,10,Fcouncils to volunteer for this as part
OL,11,Fof the first wave of changes.
